message: "If you use this software in research, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "Clinical-AI-Ops-Agent: Agentic MLOps for Autonomous Healthcare Model Monitoring"
abstract: >
  An agentic AI system that autonomously monitors deployed clinical ML models,
  detects data drift using PSI and KS statistical tests, triggers SageMaker
  retraining pipelines, validates new models against safety thresholds, and
  deploys using blue/green traffic shifting on AWS — without human intervention.
